                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h3>Why Cyber Security International?</h3></div>
                                            </div> <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_divider et_pb_divider_0 et_pb_divider_position_ et_pb_space"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_2  et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_bg_layout_light">
                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p><span>Monthly audits without you realising. We can look at your systems in place and look at protected you are from distance. We do this by adding discrete bits of passive software on each node of your network. This is really about compliance and is an integral part of ISO27001.</span></p></div>
                                            </div> <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_3  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
