                                        <div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_7  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
                                            <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_13  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2>ISO 27001 in more detail</h2></div>
                                            </div> <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_divider et_pb_divider_1 et_pb_divider_position_ et_pb_space"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_14  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>An internationally recognised standard that:</p></div>
                                            </div> <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_15  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light">
                                                <div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Helps protect and secure an organization&#8217;s data and information from risks, threats and vulnerabilities.</p>
                                                    <p>It helps design and implement a suite of information security controls to address those risks that are deemed unacceptable and mitigate others.</p>
                                                    <p>It implements a management process to ensure that the information security controls continue to meet the ongoing needs of the organization.</p>
                                                    <p>It creates an overarching information security management system (ISMS), creating cohesion of IT or data security, business continuity planning, physical security and Human Resources.</p></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div> <div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_8 et_pb_section_parallax  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
